Name: Average time from Manuscript Export Succeeded to Plagiarism Originality Report Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Total time between Manuscript Export Succeeded and SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-Reviewer Agreed after the execution of Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Total resolution time of Manuscript Export Succeeded in variants that include SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and the end of case where activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed occurs

Name: Time from Manuscript Export Succeeded to SW-AE Assign Reviewers in cases where SW-Reviewer Agreed eventually occurs
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Elapsed time between Manuscript Export Succeeded and SW-Reviewer Agreed across all process variants containing both activities
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Average waiting time to SW-Reviewer Agreed after Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Minimum time from Manuscript Export Succeeded to SW-Awaiting AE Assignment in variants leading to SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Total time it takes Manuscript Export Succeeded to be followed by any reviewer-related activity (e.g., SW-Initial Reviewer Selection) in submissions that result in SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Time of Manuscript Export Succeeded in cases that proceed to SW-EIC Accept versus those that end in SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and the end of case where activity 'SW-EIC Accept occurs

Name: Average time between Manuscript Export Succeeded and SW-Reviewer Agreed specifically in high-duration variants (performance > 1,000,000 seconds)
Metric: the average of the function base > 1000000 where base is the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and the last time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Cycle Time of Manuscript Export Succeeded measured from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to Manuscript Export Succeeded in trajectories that later include SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Total time from Manuscript Export Succeeded to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in variants where SW-Reviewer Agreed appears exactly once
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Minimum time it takes Manuscript Export Succeeded after Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation in cases that eventually reach SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'
